>>用赋值语句创建函数
>> student.name = 'John Doe';
>> student.addr1 = '123 Main Street';
>> student.city = 'Anytown';
>> student.zip = '71211';
>> student

student = 

     name: 'John Doe'
    addr1: '123 Main Street'
     city: 'Anytown'
      zip: '71211'

>> whos student
  Name         Size            Bytes  Class     Attributes

  student      1x1               774  struct      
  
 
 %用赋值语句将student这个struct 扩大
  >> student(2).name = 'Jane Q.Public'

student = 

1x2 struct array with fields:

    name
    addr1
    city
    zip

>> student(1)

ans = 

     name: 'John Doe'
    addr1: '123 Main Street'
     city: 'Anytown'
      zip: '71211'

>> student(2)

ans = 

     name: 'Jane Q.Public'
    addr1: []
     city: []
      zip: []

>> whos
  Name         Size            Bytes  Class     Attributes

  ans          1x1               418  struct              
  student      1x2               936  struct              

>> % student 现在是一个1*2的数据
>> 
>> name
Undefined function or variable 'name'.
 
 
 % name addr1 之类的为名字 ans结果为域 通过域的名字来访问域
>> student.name

ans =

John Doe


ans =

Jane Q.Public

>> 


